  "content": "      <figure>      <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/k9hyN7YA-twd6YPu491_lgjLLlQ=/150x0:1770x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/70462198/Griftlands.15.jpg\" />        <figcaption><em>Science-fantasy deckbuilder </em>Griftlands<em> is one of several titles currently discounted on the Nintendo eShop.</em></figcaption>    </figure>  <p id=\"YBzaYX\">The <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2022/3/12/22974056/nintendo-switch-top-selling-console-february-2022\">Nintendo Switch is one of the most popular consoles ever released</a>, one with an ever-expanding library of games to choose from. Odds are if a game is capable of working on the Switch’s hardware, it’s either already available or it will be soon. </p><p id=\"nuW2pm\">Thankfully, a number of games are currently receiving price breaks if you’re looking to expand your collection, including first-gen offerings like <a href=\"https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FLegend-of-Zelda-Breath-of-the-Wild-Switch-Nintendo-Digital-Download%2F800322001&amp;subid1=TheVergeDailyDealsFeb222022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><em>The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild</em></a> and remasters like <a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/diablo-iii-eternal-collection-switch/\"><em>Diablo III: Eternal Collection</em></a>. However, if you want to add some less conventional indie titles to your collection, Klei Entertainment has also discounted the deckbuilding roguelike <a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/griftlands-switch/\"><em>Griftlands</em></a> and the Tim Burton-esque survival game, <a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/dont-starve-nintendo-switch-edition-switch/\"><em>Don’t Starve</em></a>.</p><p id=\"F0kxGk\">Below, we’ve rounded up some of the deals on Nintendo Switch games. In many instances, the Nintendo eShop is typically the best place to find deals on digital downloads, especially if you prefer the indie variety, but there are some exceptions where retailers will discount titles that would otherwise be full price on Nintendo’s storefront.</p><aside id=\"nVFGs4\"><div data-anthem-component=\"readmore\" data-anthem-component-data='{\"stories\":[{\"title\":\"Here’s where you can buy a Nintendo Switch\",\"url\":\"https://www.theverge.com/21257643/nintendo-switch-lite-oled-how-to-buy-in-stock\"},{\"title\":\"Here are some must-have accessories for your new Nintendo Switch\",\"url\":\"https://www.theverge.com/22912942/best-nintendo-switch-controllers-cases-chargers-headsets-accessories\"}]}'></div></aside><div id=\"zEVgtf\"><div data-anthem-component=\"table:11175535\"></div></div><div id=\"330BZr\"><div data-anthem-component=\"productcard:11119864\" data-anthem-component-data='{\"layout\":\"full_layout\"}'></div></div><div id=\"IascM7\"><div data-anthem-component=\"productcard:9514828\" data-anthem-component-data='{\"layout\":\"full_layout\"}'></div></div><div id=\"uNIC1m\"><div data-anthem-component=\"productcard:10516697\" data-anthem-component-data='{\"layout\":\"full_layout\"}'></div></div><aside id=\"0sKMpN\"><div data-anthem-component=\"readmore\" data-anthem-component-data='{\"stories\":[{\"title\":\"The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild’s sequel is delayed to spring 2023\",\"url\":\"https://www.theverge.com/2022/3/29/23001375/the-legend-of-zelda-breath-of-the-wild-2-sequel-delay-release-date\"}]}'></div></aside><div id=\"iv1NiD\"><div data-anthem-component=\"productcard:10468219\" data-anthem-component-data='{\"layout\":\"full_layout\"}'></div></div><div id=\"ijAJuv\"><div data-anthem-component=\"productcard:9514849\" data-anthem-component-data='{\"layout\":\"full_layout\"}'></div></div><div id=\"OPOcT3\"><div data-anthem-component=\"productcard:9514842\" data-anthem-component-data='{\"layout\":\"full_layout\"}'></div></div><div id=\"NIzmPk\"><div data-anthem-component=\"productcard:10248596\" data-anthem-component-data='